Date: Fri, 17 Jul 2026 21:09:22 +0200
Subject: [PATCH 08/17] Serialize artworks.thumbnail_url

ResultArtwork never selected/exposed thumbnail_url even though the
column has existed since the database's V3 migration. Frontend now
requires it (Artwork.jsx thumbnail prop). Follows the same nullable
passthrough pattern as media_url.

pp1_collection.db refreshed from the database repo (media_url extension
fix, see database repo's migrate_v5.py).

Co-Authored-By: Claude Sonnet 5 <noreply@anthropic.com>
